comment: [Observable in enhanced video] Plumlee (POR) moves his pivot foot.
Plumlee (POR) takes a wide stance and delivers the contact to Thompson's (GSW) leg/hip on the screen.
Green (GSW) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Green (GSW) makes contact with Plumlee (POR) that affects his SQBR.
Green (GSW) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he contests Plumlee's (POR) shot attempt.
Aminu (POR) and Durant (GSW) briefly engage and separate off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Durant (GSW) moves his pivot foot.
Iguodala (GSW) sets the screen on McCollum (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Lillard (POR) was attempting a 2pt field goal when he was fouled in the act of shooting is overturned. Lillard is awarded three free throws.
McAdoo (GSW) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Lillard's (POR) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Plumlee (POR) commits a take foul on Durant (GSW).
Green (GSW) enters the lane after Thompson (GSW) releases the ball.
Plumlee (POR) places two hands on Thompson (GSW), affecting his SQBR.
Thompson (GSW) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a 3pt field goal attempt is confirmed.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
Crabbe (POR) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
Turner (POR) does not extend his arm and dislodge Thompson (GSW) from his legal guarding position.
Turner (POR) takes more than the two allowed steps after gathering the ball.
Durant (GSW) extends his arm and dislodges Turner (POR) from his legal guarding position.
Turner (POR) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Durant (GSW).
